e1f3c8eb25d970a8c0bfe85367f12","tid":876373,"uid":122513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T06:30:48.000Z","msg":"你好，這是《自殺．自療．互助舍》。看來你已累積了不少負面情緒，是嗎？人就好像氣球一樣，若積存的鬱結和壓力太多，便會有爆發的一天。何不暫時停一停，<a href=\"http://到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%88%B0%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E7%9A%84%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99www.help4suicide.com.hk&d=4pRdITrIMAcXc3kQu1NO2bIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=d42397ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>。 那裡有一些勵志故事和有趣短片，你可以隨心看看。你也可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），讓我們的義工為你加油打氣！<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！"},{"pid":"43f1ddeb7f7c4ed48a074e3c686d0d4b3af9de14","tid":876373,"uid":7915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T06:36:51.000Z","msg":"依排黑咩...？<br />\n講嚟聽下<br />\n我都係咁"},{"pid":"40182af8919138eae523d3d44b1615b0b87ed4da","tid":876373,"uid":115510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T06:45:40.000Z","msg":"自性化"},{"pid":"dd7ba440369b48d1d9a64bd7eb20905264d79ace","tid":876373,"uid":48987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T06:46:22.000Z","msg":"你出生窮家庭咪覺得受苦囉"},{"pid":"e443ec99a16c87612a79d59f62d76ba655db4668","tid":876373,"uid":211114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T06:50:53.000Z","msg":"頂住呀ching. 我䎞有呎種感覺，所以西圍去旅行，揾下意義。"},{"pid":"1c98c5e84aef5dd95a409e1b81834651a1c23a61","tid":876373,"uid":53238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T06:55:19.000Z","msg":"為左養兒防老<br />\n你認命啦"},{"pid":"8b58cd3279d2857006533786ce86c909bd547d53","tid":876373,"uid":90660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43f1ddeb7f7c4ed48a074e3c686d0d4b3af9de14","tid":876373,"uid":7915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T06:36:51.000Z","msg":"依排黑咩...？<br />\n講嚟聽下<br />\n我都係咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T14:09:19.000Z","ms